\includegraphics[width=0.48\linewidth]{I_vs_phi_JD_U_30_bis.eps}
\caption{\label{fig:simul_I_vs_phase} Simulated un-parity index $I$ as function of the phase of coupling $\varphi$ for several gains of coupling $u'/v_{ac}$ and for two jet mean velocities $\langle u \rangle=20$ m/s (right) and $\langle u \rangle=30$ m/s (left). The phase shift $\varphi_{b'/\eta}$ between the modulation of the jet width $b'$ and the jet center position $\eta$ is also indicated.}
